#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:583
msgid "What is the difference between Free and Pro?"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:589
msgid "The themes are well-made in both their free and premium versions. But there are a lot more features in the Pro edition."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:592
msgid "You may quickly alter the appearance and feel of your website with the Pro version. You can alter your websites color and typeface with a few clicks. With more customization choices, the premium version gives you greater control over the theme. In addition, the theme offers more layout options and sections than the free version."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:601
msgid "What are the advantages of upgrading to the Premium version?"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:607
msgid "In addition to the additional features and regular upgrades, the Premium version comes with premium support. Compared to the free assistance, you will receive a much faster response if you encounter any theme problems."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:616
msgid "Upgrading to the Pro version- will I lose my changes?"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:622
msgid "Your posts, pages, media, categories, and other data will all be preserved when you upgrade to the Pro theme."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:625
msgid "You will need to configure the extra features via the customizer, though, because the Pro edition has more features and options. It just takes a few minutes to complete this easy process."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:628
msgid "There is a lot of flexibility in the Pro version to accommodate future updates. As a result, it differs slightly from the free theme yet is incredibly versatile and user-friendly."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:637
msgid "How do I change the copyright text?"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:643
msgid "You can change the copyright text going to Appearance > Customize > Footer Option > And here you can find (Edit Footer Copyright Text)"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:652
msgid "Why is my theme not working well?"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:658
msgid "It could be a plugin conflict if your customizer is not loading correctly or if you are experiencing problems with the theme."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:661
msgid "Deactivate every plugin first, with the exception of those the theme suggests, to resolve the problem. After that, use \"Ctrl+Shift+R\" on Windows to force a new page load. Once the problems have been resolved, begin turning on each plugin individually, then refresh and verify your website each time. This will assist you in identifying the problematic plugin."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:664
msgid "Please get in touch with us if this was not helpful."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:673
msgid "How can I solve my issues quickly and get faster support?"
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:679
msgid "Please make sure you have updated the theme to the most recent version before sending us a support ticket for any problems. The theme update may have resolved the issue."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:682
msgid "Please try to include as much information as you can in your support ticket submission so that we can address your issue more quickly. We advise you to email us one or more screenshots that clearly illustrate the problems and include the URL of your website."
msgstr ""

#: themeinfo/pixel_cyber_security_themeinfo_page.php:685
msgid "Please be patient with us as we may have a delayed response time during the weekend."
msgstr ""

